</P>
<P>
	Same-store sales fell 2.3 percent at Penney stores only.  
</P>
<P>
	Total sales were $2.78 billion, up 6.6 percent from $2.60  
billion. 
</P>
<P>
 *Five months ended July 3: 
</P>
<P>
	Same-store sales fell 0.5 percent at Penney stores only.  
</P>
<P>
