	``As a kid, the club pro used to tell me, `If you can drive it  
pretty good and you've got a pretty good short game, you will be 
able to score,''' Doyle said. ```So don't ever pay attention to 
anybody that can't beat you.' 
</P>
<P>
	``I always have kept that to heart.''  
  	   	
</P>
</TEXT>
